{"tid":97361,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳曼聯再用破紀錄價購熱刺Alli","createTime":"2017-01-27T15:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T01:55:53.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c49f9e57cf3df7cca2b746c54db53da3e08fbb69","tid":97361,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:00:21.000Z","msg":"Tottenham Hotspur's standout performer of the season so far, Dele Alli, is being linked with a world record transfer to Manchester United, according to The Sun. The 20-year old has been heavily linked with Real Madrid over the last month but, according to a former colleague of Jorge Mendes, Jose Mourinho has identified Alli as his No. 1 target for the summer transfer window. Vincent Rodriguez, a lawyer and former agent, has also claimed that Spurs would be willing to sell the England midfielder -- but only for a world-record &pound;100m fee.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m0.joe.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/17111539/Screen-Shot-2017-01-17-at-11.15.16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm0.joe.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F17111539%2FScreen-Shot-2017-01-17-at-11.15.16.png&h=18d4dd23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b00f059a2789385eb7d45281503a27a78ea94e13","tid":97361,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"唔緊要，重可以用賣c 朗既錢"},{"pid":"4a1dd46ea5f35afad8b4ed7538193788599a232b","tid":97361,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:18:41.000Z","msg":"咁臭串<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a0be6cb511da979e326b5de79e40742eb39277","tid":97361,"uid":24024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔緊要，重可以用賣c 朗既錢</blockquote><br />\n碧咸個筆都未洗哂"},{"pid":"3adf2898ff3bb7c1a860f8eb6cbdff63b022b48e","tid":97361,"uid":15370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T18: